11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2-122.4 of Title 47, unless
14 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 A. The Oklahoma Department of Emergency Management shall
16 promulgate rules to create the Canine Cooperative Grant Program to
17 provide financial assistance to state, county, and municipal law
18 enforcement entities and fire departments for the acquisition and
19 training of law enforcement canines and search, rescue, and recovery
20 canines and medical expenses for the canines related to injuries
21 sustained while in the line of service; provided, canines shall be
22 trained in accordance with state law and agency standards and shall
23 be specifically allocated for law enforcement officers and fire
24 departments.
