3 E. Subject to the availability of funds, the program shall make
4 grants for the reimbursement of medical expenses for canines injured
5 in the line of service with state, county, or municipal law
6 enforcement or a fire department.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
